# Place the M5Stack-shipped ESP32-C6 esp_hosted slave firmware here.
#
# File: ESP32C6-WiFi-SDIO-Interface-V1.4.1-96bea3a_0x0.bin
# Source: https://github.com/m5stack/M5Tab5-UserDemo/tree/main/platforms/tab5/wifi_c6_fw
#
# This binary is flashed to the `slave_fw` partition (see partitions.csv) so
# the ESP32-P4 can load the C6 co-processor firmware over SDIO at boot and
# provide WiFi. It is NOT committed to this repo (see .gitignore) — download
# it from the M5Tab5-UserDemo repo and drop it here before flashing, or use
# the M5Stack flash.sh script to program the C6 directly (see README.md).
